## 封装加载图片的promise  
```js
let loadImg = (src)=>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        // write your code here
    })
}
```

student_answer:
let loadImg = (src)=>{
    return new Promise((resolve, reject)=>{
        const image=new Image();
        image.onload(()=>{
        resolve(image);
        })
       image.onerror(()=>{
        reject(new Error(src+'加载错误'));
        })
  		image.src=src;
    })
}
